Hey guys! I've opened up a brand new bunnyhop map! This map has 4 levels and 1 bonus surf to bhop. This map also has music
eDIT - Ants
Ed Sheeran - I see fire
Vexare - Clockmaker

Fully functioning teleports a "backwards telehop". Map has obviously some custom textures made by Dev. Special thanks to Joey7 for helping me a ton on learning how to map and helping me with my mistakes. Special thanks to AMP and Alvarez from TitanClan for helping me test the map on their private server! Hope you guys enjoy,

-KaMiKaZi
